lead_paragraph: The most dominant runner at Jamaica's national track and field championships this summer was not a superstar sprinter like Usain Bolt, Yohan Blake or Veronica Campbell-Brown.

headline.print_headline: After the Sprinters, Jamaica Seeking Track and Field Depth
